parameters.customQuery:
SELECT distinct claimanttransaction.SystemId, claimanttransaction.ParentId, claimanttransaction.CMMContainer, claimanttransaction.Id, claimanttransaction.TransactionCd, claimanttransaction.StatusCd, claimanttransaction.PaymentStatus, claimanttransaction.PaymentStatusDt, claimanttransaction.PaymentTypeCd, claimanttransaction.PaymentMethodCd, claimanttransaction.PaymentAccountCd, claimanttransaction.PaymentReference, claimanttransaction.PayToName, claimanttransaction.PayToClaimantInd, claimanttransaction.PayToProviderInd, claimanttransaction.ProviderRef, claimanttransaction.PayToInterestInd, claimanttransaction.InterestCd, claimanttransaction.InterestIdRef, claimanttransaction.PayToOverrideInd, claimanttransaction.RecoveryCheckNumber, claimanttransaction.RecoveryCheckDt, claimanttransaction.RecoveryPaidBy, claimanttransaction.ClaimTransactionHistoryRef, claimanttransaction.Memo, claimanttransaction.MemoCd, claimanttransaction.Comment, claimanttransaction.PaidAmt, claimanttransaction.ReserveAmt, claimanttransaction.RecoveryAmt, claimanttransaction.ExpectedRecoveryAmt, claimanttransaction.ClassificationCd, claimanttransaction.SequenceNumber, claimanttransaction.TransactionNumber, claimanttransaction.TransactionDt, claimanttransaction.TransactionTm, claimanttransaction.TransactionUser, claimanttransaction.ClaimantTransactionRef, claimanttransaction.BookDt, claimanttransaction.PrinterTemplateIdRef, claimanttransaction.RecoveryCheckAmt, claimanttransaction.AutomatedPaymentInd, claimanttransaction.VoidAllowedInd, claimanttransaction.SubrogationIdRef, claimanttransaction.ServicePeriodStartDt, claimanttransaction.SystemCheckReference, claimanttransaction.ServicePeriodEndDt, claimanttransaction.ReasonCd, claimanttransaction.PayToPriorOverrideInd, claimanttransaction.DaysPaid, claimanttransaction.WeeksPaid, claimanttransaction.DenialReason, claimanttransaction.NonConsecutivePeriod, claimanttransaction.LumpSumPaymentCd, claimanttransaction.RecoveryType, claimanttransaction.InvoiceNumber, claimanttransaction.RowId 
FROM
 claimanttransaction where cmmcontainer='claim' and systemid in (select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where  concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' and
 cmmcontainer='Claim')
